txt.en: The Jangovar are harassing Hammerstead, attempting to steal the dwarves' weapons. Defeat their leaders to throw them into disarray!
The Jangovar are attacking Hammerstead!\n\nYou should defeat the Jangovar leaders.
You should talk to Lóssi, who can be found defending Hammerstead.
'I have seen the Easterlings' leaders out there, barking orders at the rest of these louts. We are pinned down here, but perhaps you can make your way to them and cut the head off this snake!'
'Good work! With the leaders defeated, the rest will fall into disarray and scatter before us!'
